init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He asks his wife if she has seen the car.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The fathers are worried that they might not be the "#1 Dad" anymore.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soon, even vehicles that aren't cars are sporting "#1 Dad" on them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's been two weeks since this whole thing started.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The country is very concerned about this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Meanwhile, the #1 Dad is out for a walk.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Suddenly, he sees a mug sitting on the sidewalk.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It has "#1 Dad" printed across it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The #1 Dad smiles and picks up the mug.
